            "title": "滬指開市升1點 深成指跌14點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段變動不大，上證綜指以4053點開市，升1點或0.05%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14870點，跌14點或0.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌1點或0.03%，開報4727點；創業板指數開市報3657點，跌20點或0.57%。</p>\n</div>",
