        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段反彈 恒指微升44點報26204點 美團逆市低開0.75%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">儘管國際期油價格抽升，日韓等亞洲主要股市今早初段依然造好，港股開市初段亦跟隨外圍反彈。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數開市報26204點，升44點或0.17%。恒生科技指數開報5059點，升16點或0.34%；國企指數以8856點開市，升11點或0.13%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股互有升跌，滙控(00005)開報142.5元，升0.71%；友邦(01299)開報81.65元，升0.06%。騰訊(00700)開報509.5元，跌0.2%；小米(01810)開報32.02元，升0.06%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">央視新聞上周五報道，市場監管局向7家電商平台「幽靈外賣」系列處以行政處分，合共罰款約36.17億元人民幣，其中涉美團(03690)、京東(09618)、阿里巴巴(09988)旗下淘寶閃購等。美團今早逆市低開0.75%，以85.85元開市；阿里巴巴開報135.7元，也跌0.51%；京東則高開0.57%，報123.3元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15893887-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%8744%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126204%e9%bb%9e-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%98%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e4%bd%8e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-20 09:29:38",
